# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
 The code effectively adds two numbers represented as linked lists and returns the result as a new linked list. The reverse function is used to simplify the addition process by reversing the linked lists before performing the addition of digits.
# Approach
